# No backend configuration required — campaign state syncs peer-to-peer via
# WebRTC (crdtbus) and persists locally in the browser (IndexedDB).
#
# Peers find each other through a PeerJS signaling server. The default is the
# free public PeerJS cloud; point this at your own peerjs-server deployment
# for reliability (hostname only, HTTPS assumed):
#
# VITE_PEERJS_HOST=0.peerjs.com
